Title: Dirac Operator on a disk with global boundary conditions

Authors: H. Falomir, R. E. Gamboa Sarav\'\i and E. M. Santangelo

Comments: RevTeX, 11 pages. References added

Journal-ref: J.Math.Phys. 39 (1998) 532-544

We compute the functional determinant for a Dirac operator in the presence ofan Abelian gauge field on a bidimensional disk, under global boundaryconditions of the type introduced by Atiyah-Patodi-Singer. We also discuss theconnection between our result and the index theorem.